## Step 6 üëÅÔ∏è

::::{.columns}

:::{.column width="50%"}


- Peepers are just two circles at a fixed location. 
- 5% (1/6 of ghost) radius
- A lot down (13%) and a little bit to the left (5%)
- Then add a shadow (the other eye) 14% to the right.
- *Phew!*

:::

:::{.column width="50%"}

```{.css filename="styles.css"}
